{"tid":2311330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美駐港總領事館：對特區政治迫害社運人士不寒而慄","createTime":"2020-12-04T03:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T04:25:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f48e45b931d9f4b2e86518de9decd34715a1c45","tid":2311330,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:47:12.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國駐港澳總領事館發表聲明，指對特區政治迫害社運人士感到不寒而慄。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指特區透過法院令異見人士噤聲，再次證明中共獨裁及害怕言論及思想自由，香港過去自由和開放，造就了黃之鋒、周庭、林朗彥及黎智英等和平的社運人士，香港市民享有基本法及中英聯合聲明保障的權利，歷史會記下他們為此抵抗中共的精神，美國會一如以往與盟友合作，捍衛港人的權利及自由。"},{"pid":"51a323840fac7214cf223bdbfeb3775701d614af","tid":2311330,"uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=415314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415314&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=8067e8f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415314&h=b74566a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=415314</a>"},{"pid":"974df6d66169261ca4a59a67b154816237ccdfbb","tid":2311330,"uid":41458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"出招啦等biden 上場就含得撚"},{"pid":"8e99c55794249c4a92c33d63d04dce999d98bc54","tid":2311330,"uid":222614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:49:40.000Z","msg":"香港人表示對拜登等人一眾叛國賊咁明目張膽表示不寒而慄"},{"pid":"cc67fd516a7f3d1b47684dade0d62481efc0d47c","tid":2311330,"uid":280020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"一年之間變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cca674e4370d5156c6523dcc01f6c46be3c99d","tid":231133